          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/hi_dheerajjangra17/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex items-center gap-3 text-ink/60 dark:text-dark-ink/60 hover:text-ink dark:hover:text-dark-ink transition-colors no-underline">
